#. <html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta content="Pali text from the Mahāsaṅgīti Tipiṭaka Buddhavasse 2500" name="description"><title></title></head><body><div id="text" lang="pi"><section class="sutta" id="pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:1.1"
msgid "Theravāda Vinaya"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:2.1"
msgid "Mahāvibhaṅga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:3.1"
msgid "Pācittiyakaṇḍa"
msgstr "The chapter on confession (<i lang=\"pi\">pācittiya</i>)"

#. </p><p> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:4.1"
msgid "Bhūtagāmavagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:5.1"
msgid "18. Vehāsakuṭisikkhāpada"
msgstr "Monks’ Confession 18: the training rule on upper stories"

#. </h1></div><h2>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:6.1"
msgid ""
msgstr "Origin story"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.46"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pc.18.1"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="BD.2.254"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa443"></a> <span class="var" hidden>viharati → eko heṭṭhā (?)</span> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:6.2"
msgid "Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in the Jeta Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:6.3"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena dve bhikkhū saṃghike vihāre uparivehāsakuṭiyā eko heṭṭhā viharati, eko upari."
msgstr "At that  time two monks were staying in a dwelling with an upper story belonging to the Order, one staying below and one above."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:6.4"
msgid "Uparimo bhikkhu āhaccapādakaṃ mañcaṃ sahasā abhinisīdi."
msgstr "The monk above sat down suddenly on a bed with detachable legs."

#. <span class="var" hidden>nippatitvā → nipatitvā (bj) | patitvā (s1-3) | nippaṭitvā (pts1)</span> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:6.5"
msgid "Mañcapādo nippatitvā heṭṭhimassa bhikkhuno matthake avatthāsi."
msgstr "A leg fell off and hit the monk below on the head."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:6.6"
msgid "So bhikkhu vissaramakāsi."
msgstr "He cried out."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:6.7"
msgid "Bhikkhū upadhāvitvā taṃ bhikkhuṃ etadavocuṃ—"
msgstr "Monks came rushing to"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:6.8"
msgid "“kissa tvaṃ, āvuso, vissaramakāsī”ti?"
msgstr "and asked him why,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:6.9"
msgid "Atha kho so bhikkhu bhikkhūnaṃ etamatthaṃ ārocesi."
msgstr "and he told them what had happened."

#. </p><p> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:6.10"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū appicchā … pe …"
msgstr "The monks of few desires …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:6.11"
msgid "te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "complained and criticized him,"

#. </p><p><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa444"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:6.12"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma bhikkhu saṃghike vihāre uparivehāsakuṭiyā āhaccapādakaṃ mañcaṃ sahasā abhinisīdissatī”ti."
msgstr "“How can a monk sit down suddenly on a bed with detachable legs on an upper story in a dwelling belonging to the Order?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:7.1"
msgid "Atha kho te bhikkhū taṃ bhikkhuṃ anekapariyāyena vigarahitvā bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ … pe …"
msgstr "After criticizing that monk in many ways, they told the Master.…"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:7.2"
msgid "“saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, bhikkhu, saṃghike vihāre uparivehāsakuṭiyā āhaccapādakaṃ mañcaṃ sahasā abhinisīdasī”ti?"
msgstr "“Is it true, monk, that you did this?”"

#. </p><p> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:7.3"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

#. </p><p> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:7.4"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha rebuked him, “…"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:7.5"
msgid "kathañhi nāma tvaṃ, moghapurisa, saṃghike vihāre uparivehāsakuṭiyā āhaccapādakaṃ mañcaṃ sahasā abhinisīdissasi."
msgstr "Foolish man, how can you sit down suddenly on a bed with detachable legs on a upper story in a dwelling belonging to the Order?"

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="BD.2.255"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:7.6"
msgid "Netaṃ, moghapurisa, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:7.7"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:"

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:8.1"
msgid ""
msgstr "Final ruling"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa445"></a>
#. <strong class="rule"><span class="note" hidden>I am here taking <i lang="pi">kuṭi</i> to refer to the upper story itself, rather than the whole building, which already has the separate name <i lang="pi">vihāra</i>.</span> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:8.2"
msgid "“Yo pana bhikkhu saṃghike vihāre uparivehāsakuṭiyā āhaccapādakaṃ mañcaṃ vā pīṭhaṃ vā abhinisīdeyya vā abhinipajjeyya vā, pācittiyan”ti."
msgstr "‘If a monk sits down or lies down on a bed or a bench with detachable legs on an upper story in a dwelling belonging to the Order, he commits an offense entailing confession.’”"

#. </strong> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:8.3"
msgid "(<em>18</em>:<strong>67</strong>)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:9.1"
msgid ""
msgstr "Definitions"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pc.18.2"></a>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pc.18.2.1"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa446"></a><strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:9.2"
msgid "Yo panāti"
msgstr "A:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:9.3"
msgid "yo yādiso … pe …"
msgstr "whoever …"

#. </span>
#. <strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:9.4"
msgid "bhikkhūti"
msgstr "Monk:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:9.5"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr "…The monk who has been given the full ordination by a complete Order through a procedure consisting of one motion and three announcements that is unchallengeable and fit to stand—"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:9.6"
msgid "ayaṃ imasmiṃ atthe adhippeto bhikkhūti."
msgstr "this sort of monk is meant in this case."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a>
#. <a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa447"></a><strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:10.1"
msgid "Saṃghiko nāma"
msgstr "A dwelling belonging to the Order:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:10.2"
msgid "vihāro saṃghassa dinno hoti pariccatto."
msgstr "given to the Order, given up to the Order."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="6"></a>
#. <a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa448"></a><strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:11.1"
msgid "Vehāsakuṭi nāma"
msgstr "An upper story:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:11.2"
msgid "majjhimassa purisassa asīsaghaṭṭā."
msgstr "a man of average height does not hit his head."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="7"></a>
#. <a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa449"></a><strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:12.1"
msgid "Āhaccapādako nāma mañco"
msgstr "A bed with detachable legs:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:12.2"
msgid "aṅge vijjhitvā ṭhito hoti."
msgstr "inserting the limbs, it stands."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="8"></a>
#. <a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa450"></a><strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:13.1"
msgid "Āhaccapādakaṃ nāma pīṭhaṃ"
msgstr "A bench with detachable legs:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:13.2"
msgid "aṅge vijjhitvā ṭhitaṃ hoti."
msgstr "inserting the limbs, it stands."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="9"></a>
#. <a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa451"></a><strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:14.1"
msgid "Abhinisīdeyyāti"
msgstr "Sits down:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:14.2"
msgid "tasmiṃ abhinisīdati, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr "if he sits down on it, he commits an offense entailing confession."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="10"></a>
#. <a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa452"></a><strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:15.1"
msgid "Abhinipajjeyyāti"
msgstr "Lies down:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:15.2"
msgid "tasmiṃ abhinipajjati, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr "if he lies down on it, he commits an offense entailing confession."

#. </span>
#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:16.1"
msgid ""
msgstr "Permutations"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="11"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pc.18.2.2"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa453"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:16.2"
msgid "Saṃghike saṃghikasaññī uparivehāsakuṭiyā āhaccapādakaṃ mañcaṃ vā pīṭhaṃ vā abhinisīdati vā abhinipajjati vā, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr "If it belongs to the Order, and he perceives it as belonging to the Order, and he sits down or lies down on a bed or a bench with detachable legs on the upper story, he commits an offense entailing confession."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:16.3"
msgid "Saṃghike vematiko … pe …"
msgstr "If it belongs to the Order, but he is unsure if it does …"

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="BD.2.256"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:16.4"
msgid "saṃghike puggalikasaññī uparivehāsakuṭiyā āhaccapādakaṃ mañcaṃ vā pīṭhaṃ vā abhinisīdati vā abhinipajjati vā, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr "If it belongs to the Order, but he perceives it as belonging to an individual, and he sits down or lies down on a bed or a bench with detachable legs on the upper story, he commits an offense entailing confession."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="12"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa454"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:17.1"
msgid "Puggalike saṃghikasaññī, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If it belongs to an individual, but he perceives it as belonging to the Order, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:17.2"
msgid "Puggalike vematiko, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If it belongs to an individual, but he is unsure if it does, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:17.3"
msgid "Puggalike puggalikasaññī aññassa puggalike, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If it belongs to an individual, and he perceives it as belonging to an individual, but that individual is not himself, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:17.4"
msgid "Attano puggalike, anāpatti."
msgstr "If it belongs to himself, there is no offense."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:18.1"
msgid ""
msgstr "Non-offenses"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="13"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pc.18.2.3"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa455"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:18.2"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr "There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:18.3"
msgid "avehāsakuṭiyā      "
msgstr "if there is no upper story;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:18.4"
msgid "sīsaghaṭṭāya"
msgstr "if the upper story is so low that one hits the head;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:18.5"
msgid "heṭṭhā aparibhogaṃ hoti,"
msgstr "if the lower story is not in use;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:18.6"
msgid "padarasañcitaṃ hoti,"
msgstr "if the upper story has floorboards;"

#. <span class="note" hidden><i lang="pi">Dinnā</i>.</span> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:18.7"
msgid "paṭāṇi dinnā hoti,"
msgstr "if bolts to fasten the legs have been applied,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:18.8"
msgid "tasmiṃ ṭhito gaṇhati vā laggeti vā,"
msgstr "if he stands on it to get hold of something or to put something up;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:18.9"
msgid "ummattakassa,"
msgstr "if he is insane;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:18.10"
msgid "ādikammikassāti."
msgstr "if he is the first offender."

#. </p><hr><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="14"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa456"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc18:19.1"
msgid "Vehāsakuṭisikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr "The eighth rule, the training rule on upper stories, is finished."

